wmr</a> 写道 "<i>Bart Simpson老师Edna Krabappel的配音演员<a target="_blank" href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-24690452">Marcia Wallace于70岁去世</a>。她配音的角色将不再继续。卫报上标出了<a target="_blank" href="http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2013/oct/28/marcia-wallace-edna-krabappel-best-simpsons-episodes">她最好的剧集</a>。Marcia死于肺炎并发症。</i>"